| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4687 — Recovery Inhibition (noescape)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c4cb8cb8-5c10-551b-abd1-7da0b0d7921f"
